>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  </Fragment>
  <section class="hero-section bg-dark" data-theme="dark">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">HOME</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <a href="/specialized-translation/">SPECIALIZED</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <span class="current">DIGITAL</span>
      </nav>

      <h1>Website Localization Services in Dubai</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Arabic SEO & Digital Content</p>
      <div class="hero-intro">
        <p>Website localization for Arabic markets requires technical precision beyond translation. Every RTL layout, Arabic SEO keyword, and UI string we deliver for <a href="/locations/dubai/">Dubai</a> and MENA audiences must work seamlessly across devices. Our localization specialists combine linguistic expertise with digital marketing knowledge to transform your online presence.</p>

        <table class="hero-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Requirement</th><th>Standard Provider</th><th>OnlineTranslation.ae</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
        <tr><td>RTL formatting</td><td>Mirror English layout</td><td>Native Arabic UX design</td></tr>
